opennlp.ccg.alignment
Class AbstractEncodingScheme

java.lang.Object
  opennlp.ccg.alignment.AbstractEncodingScheme
All Implemented Interfaces:
EncodingScheme
Direct Known Subclasses:
MosesEncodingScheme, NAACLEncodingScheme
public abstract class AbstractEncodingScheme
extends Object
implements EncodingScheme

Abstract class for implementing encoding schemes. This base class provides a constructor taking all the necessary arguments for implementing EncodingScheme, and gives getter methods for all of them, as required.

Author:
Scott Martin
See Also:
